companyName: iShares Core S&P U.S. Growth ETF
description:
The investment seeks to track the investment results of the S&P 900 Growth Index (the "underlying index").
 The fund generally invests at least 90% of its assets in securities of the underlying index and in depositary receipts representing securities of the underlying index. The underlying index measures the performance of the large- and mid- capitalization growth sector of the U.S. equity market.
